From b0fb3e3eadd015f153c78c47596e46ccef2a1902 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Julius Schwartzenberg <julius.schwartzenberg@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 18 Nov 2024 21:46:39 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] add max_aneg_speed code from devolo's sources

---
 .../ath79/dts/ar9344_devolo_dlan_wifi.dtsi    |  50 ++++
 .../generic/files/drivers/net/phy/ar8327.c    | 242 +++++++++++++++++-
 .../generic/files/drivers/net/phy/ar8327.h    |  30 +++
